HOOKS IN REACT NATIVE

What are hooks?
All the features that was possible in Class based Components and not in Functional Components, With the help of Hooks, we can do all the things
in Functional Components that we could do in Class based Components.

* Introduced in react 16.8

* They let us use state and other features without writing a Class.

* Starts with 'use' keyword.

* Hooks cannot be used in Class based components. You can use it in only Functional Components.


